ken=\"r6WR9u6fAZPDcfU4/3gP2OygIm1uh177\"; session=\"1509265:1:YBAa_gGPtb0x1m_CjoNf4MgBhDG2mDJG.em\"```\n\n\n\nThanks,\n@sameerphad72\n\n## Impact\n\nAttacker Can Login To Victim Account Without Any Login Details Via Cookies. :-)","weakness":{"id":27,"name":"Improper Authentication - Generic"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":380556,"file_name":"liberapay.mp4","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/000/380/556/bcd72ffcaea5975db0873696ac27ca9c4a429584/liberapay.mp4?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22liberapay.mp4%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27liberapay.mp4\u0026response-content-type=video%2Fwebm\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQQJGGPZOK%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T094123Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECgaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJGMEQCIFRoAkK2pIoeVGJggpRS3B%2FoVx5w%2B%2FZX6d2wSeXuXd%2FYAiAT7vegUQKGuzO78%2BbrWzHyxesFEpwqQsp6pj0Y7gZ9Uiq7BQjx%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F8BEAMaDDAxMzYxOTI3NDg0OSIMTy0ynErS6iTFn%2BkpKo8F3cheRObzYv0gbwBUz%2B3MVI6c45pZ9CCyuHtuRZclI0PFK9NtYlHjI54GUsLtROyQREZvmbZWJUtdhkYzD0wAJgVz8Onb9BiGi%2B%2FemsI6fX64tZJTXchenfQhzpdWlwlq3ddAcz8%2Fg9pSE8%2FXRdqKlkHIXXimhHTRFvM8NTVgkICpR%2F1B%2FMH%2ByuWQmo2VLYjQlP50CxvRfGzUO6Ky6Tk1SskZa4l7zDrTfYkaFSSO1czWhxEPP8fTUM8KYoeohbGilZ1xexgyCqM%2B5rCsNyJnIWVGaabx%2BdArs7F9ZLf4b%2FjjUH8QsYppF6vbkLwN4I7SlIjTLzwurNB%2BCd4BEIMhsnpixhyiysgobrk9ldFDB2jxCcw5gj4Dgp5rcPdiz4n9foj2iA28w1G13zfy35NKyHzlO79OjVZ%2FF9XHRzijp%2BRKXcggEDS7%2FQdtc9uKzWfgml0r61FGWjuCTjufuQdbPjI3MaP8u%2BC6DyPDsYxxRROpbvXuKrJ56zgQqxG4tHVRz%2FQYVzGe2yvSasPcp%2B7eg4%2FPLoNclU2EanEhuG%2F7bM3JuQpp%2FXjKDFy21FnBK8U49kU3UezCLlPr4Vg7EAIp87qhHKvswYKkvNkkyiLfi%2FQSNMOoZ4TQQAv%2FXRYLYfCqjpMMj3aT9IjNRGqVplZfRQt4WvqQ7XSrR7WQMlxHlBrkA7sb1rQD265C9E10VW9it0QrL7OM3ppGxeThJbFvwmafWK6d8I4d3NqONj1IOBFAIx3H1qtloGQQbIcT6vryOXeBFFWX1c9lwrQiB%2B8Rbs9z5gSFa